{"type": "article", "id": 28336, "title": "自行车灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-17T06:40:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 62, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702161822Eph7wdVnNtQKYlO0.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>为了让骑手们在夜晚也能安心骑行，市面上出现了许多大大小小的自行车灯，但它们往往会放置在自行车前方正中，在视觉上造成了一定的遮挡，携带起来也并不是很方便。设计师 Octavian Richea 将灯具和握柄结合在一起，推出了这款名为 Lumma 的产品。除了前灯和尾灯之外，内置的激光还能在路面上投射出两道红线，显著提升了可见度，并且营造出了一条专属于你的车道。Lumma 的重量仅为 180 克，内置的锂电池充满后可以持续使用 50 小时或者最多六周的常规使用时间。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/grips-that-combine-all-lights-needed-on-the-bike#/\">众筹链接</a>，最低价为 45 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161818Vf0XBwTd7Msmutjl.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161818KD679OAmcd342wJn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702161819FmxlNnXQ3kuWEqKT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021618201tsLgZ7rakifCl4b.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}